CFB Data Teams Examples

Saiem Gilani

Source: vignettes/cfbd_teams.Rmd
cfbd_teams.Rmd

Load and Install Packages 

if (!requireNamespace('pacman', quietly = TRUE)){
  install.packages('pacman')
}
pacman::p_load(dplyr,tidyr, gt)
pacman::p_load_current_gh("sportsdataverse/cfbfastR")

Get Team Matchup History (Total Record) 

cfbd_team_matchup_records("Texas", "Oklahoma")
## ── Team matchup record from CollegeFootballData.com ────────── cfbfastR 1.9.3 ──
## ℹ Data updated: 2022-09-23 03:26:37 UTC
